{"tid":2431034,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，止蝕有咩好笑，SH有咩好笑","createTime":"2021-03-03T10:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T13:32:31.000Z","uid":82310,"like":45,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"78acacda25e4fb6f9dc8424cfbb49fe09b6ab89f","tid":2431034,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"大概前年 11 月開始<br />\n嚟財經台搵下交易靈感咁<br />\n受台上面巴打帶歇 return 都高過契媽少少<br />\n但後來，我諗係近呢半年，覺得財經台有少少唔同咗<br />\n最直接就係止蝕同SH之間互相唔同意對方<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得咁樣睇，<br />\n每人嘅風險承受能力唔同投資策略都唔同<br />\n咁有人嘅做法係覺得隻股失去咗動力，就會果斷止蝕<br />\n有人係抱緊好股，一概SH到尾而唔 Time the market<br />\n我覺得兩種投資策略都各自係啱<br />\n我亦都好多謝「社工」提醒 cut loss<br />\n我 GME 蝕住走（後來好似有翻生？）但冇後悔"},{"pid":"ecfab55b795181b4c2f64a6fe08b6583d81f46b4","tid":2431034,"uid":102255,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"都係個個道理，呢度好多人自己賺都唔夠睇人仆街咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cca47a4fa5187ca1f9667edc772e7185bef227f","tid":2431034,"uid":26015,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲都以踩踏其他人獲得自豪感"},{"pid":"aab68bbb5113041ae98eb012efdd1a322fdc7b8f","tid":2431034,"uid":215755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"左一巴右一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168193e6c51d76130fec025c142bcbbbcfa24ec8","tid":2431034,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"放左GME 唔38 溝己經失敗啦"},{"pid":"0c769a5d291ddd9f16727e7f6c4d199d6b883c36","tid":2431034,"uid":166785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"睇跌先止 既然覺跌又唔敢買淡<br />\n不如話止蝕撚廢"},{"pid":"1adab59ffe5bcd1ed73073b560cd7426524f48a8","tid":2431034,"uid":342873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"財經台唯一清流post 好同意"},{"pid":"09a5545d4ef892a216036f1d9c7c0f9e9586c250","tid":2431